    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Type&nbsp;</strong>disease (fungus);&nbsp;<strong>Save&nbsp;</strong>Fortitude DC 13;</p>\n<p><strong>Onset</strong>&nbsp;<span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListDiseases_ctl00_LabelName\">1 day</span>;&nbsp;<strong>Frequency&nbsp;</strong>1/day</p>\n<p><strong>Effect&nbsp;</strong>-4 on Perception checks, target is permanently&nbsp;<a class=\"entity-link\" style=\"color: #ff6400; border: none; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background: none;\" draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf1.conditions\" data-id=\"coxrkb6qUKBZvVxP\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">blinded</span></a><a draggable=\"false\" data-pack=\"pf1.conditions\" data-id=\"coxrkb6qUKBZvVxP\">&nbsp;</a>if fails 3 saves</p>\n<p><strong>Cure&nbsp;</strong>2 consecutive saves&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>This mold tends to begin growing in the folds of the eyelids. Over the course of a day, it spreads to cover the eyelids and begins to cover the eyeball. If left untreated, this mold can cause the character to go permanently blind.</p>",
